              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <p class="text-lg text-[#FFA985] font-semibold">
          <Icon name="tag" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" />Book both services and save 10-15%!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Open House Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50 px-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 p-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FFA985]/20 to-[#FFC67D]/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <Icon name="home" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] text-3xl" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#333333] mb-4">Selling Your Tuscumbia Home?</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              First impressions matter in real estate. Professional cleaning before listing photos and open houses helps your Tuscumbia home show its best. We focus on the details buyers notice—sparkling kitchens, gleaming bathrooms, and fresh, inviting spaces throughout.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">
              Ask about our real estate preparation packages for sellers and agents!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Local Expert Guide -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#333333] mb-8">Event Cleaning in Tuscumbia: What Local Hosts Need to Know</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 space-y-6">
        <p>Tuscumbia's event calendar is one of the most distinctive in North Alabama, anchored by celebrations that draw visitors from across the country and create a genuine community identity around hosting and gathering. The Helen Keller Festival in June — held each year near the birthplace of Tuscumbia's most famous native — brings thousands of visitors to Colbert County, and many Tuscumbia families host out-of-town guests during festival week. The preparation required for this level of hospitality goes well beyond everyday tidying: guest bedrooms need genuine deep cleaning, bathrooms need inspection-level detail, and every common area that guests will see needs to make the right impression. Our event cleaning service is specifically designed to get Tuscumbia homes to the hosting standard that a week of out-of-town company requires. We understand the festival calendar and build our scheduling around it — which is why booking early for June is essential if you want our service during Helen Keller Festival week.</p>
        <p>The Miracle Worker outdoor drama, performed each summer at the Helen Keller Birthplace and Ivy Green, creates another concentrated wave of hosting activity in Tuscumbia every season. Families who travel to see the production — some returning year after year as part of a summer tradition — often stay with Tuscumbia residents, and the combination of summer heat, outdoor activities, and extended houseguests creates a unique set of cleaning challenges that our team knows well. Alabama summers bring humidity that accelerates surface grime and bathroom mildew, and homes that are constantly moving in and out through back doors accumulate tracked-in dirt faster than hosts expect. Our summer event cleaning addresses these seasonal realities — not just surface presentation, but the deeper cleaning that makes a home genuinely fresh for guests navigating the heat and activity of a Shoals summer visit.</p>
        <p>Dickens Christmas in downtown Tuscumbia transforms the city's character each December and creates the area's single biggest hosting season of the year. Families decorate extensively, invite relatives and friends from across the region, and expect their homes to reflect the warmth and craftsmanship of the holiday season. The gap between a home that looks decorated and one that is also genuinely clean — baseboards wiped, kitchen surfaces detailed, bathrooms sanitized to the standard a guest actually notices — is exactly what professional pre-event cleaning provides. Tuscumbia hosts who rely on us for their Dickens Christmas preparation consistently report that the combination of their own decorating effort and our cleaning detail creates the welcoming environment they want their home to project during the most-visited season of the year. We recommend booking by early November to secure December dates.</p>
        <p>Tuscumbia's connection to the broader Shoals music heritage adds a distinctive dimension to event hosting in this small Alabama city. FAME Studios in nearby Muscle Shoals, the legacy of the Muscle Shoals Sound Studio, and the W.C. Handy connection that runs through the Shoals' musical identity attract music industry professionals and enthusiasts who sometimes gather in area homes for industry events, listening sessions, and informal gatherings that celebrate this community's remarkable creative legacy. Whether you're hosting a house concert, a music business dinner, or simply friends who appreciate the Shoals' place in American music history, your home's presentation matters. Our event cleaning ensures that whatever draws people to Tuscumbia and the broader Shoals — the music, the history, the community ties — your home is the right backdrop for the gathering.</p>
        <p>Homes in Tuscumbia's established neighborhoods and along Wilson Lake and Spring Creek often serve as primary entertainment venues for extended family reunions and multi-day gatherings that require sustained hosting across an entire weekend or longer. The challenge these extended events present isn't just the preparation — it's the post-event restoration when a home has been in constant use for multiple days. Our post-event cleaning service is designed precisely for this scenario: arriving after the last guest departs to restore your home from actively-hosting condition to the baseline cleanliness you expect in your daily life. Furniture returned to place, kitchen surfaces deep-cleaned after days of continuous use, bathrooms sanitized after a full weekend of guest traffic — the thorough restoration that turns a well-used home back into your personal living space without requiring the host to spend their recovery day cleaning.</p>
        <p>Alabama and Auburn game days carry a cultural weight in Tuscumbia and across the Shoals that transforms football Saturdays into genuine community social occasions. Pre-game cleaning sets the stage properly: clean surfaces, vacuumed and mopped floors, prepared bathrooms that are ready for guests, and a kitchen set up for the food and drinks that Shoals game day hosting reliably involves. Post-game cleaning handles the aftermath of those long hours of enthusiastic celebration — the spills, the displaced furniture, the kitchen mess from a day of cooking and snacking, and the accumulated state that a well-enjoyed Saturday leaves behind. We handle both ends of the game day timeline so that hosting a watch party on Saturday doesn't cost you the rest of your weekend. Call 256-826-1100 to book your next Tuscumbia event cleaning — pre-event, post-event, or the bundle that covers both.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQs -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-[#333333] mb-4">
        Frequently Asked <span class="gold-gradient">Questions</span>
      </h2>
